      "outputs": [],

      "metadata": {
        "id": "v9HUlOGt1fvU"
      },
      "outputs": [],
      "source": [
        "train_datagen=ImageDataGenerator(rescale=1./255,zoom_range=0.2,horizontal_flip=True,vertical_flip=False)"

      "execution_count": null,
      "metadata": {
        "id": "F8iwPX4c15LH"
      },

      "source": [

      "source": [

    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "execution_count": null,
      "metadata": {
        "id": "YDNPGqCr3QGm"
      },
      "outputs": [],
      "source": [
        "from tensorflow.keras.models import Sequential\n",
        "from tensorflow.keras.layers import Dense,Convolution2D,MaxPooling2D,Flatten,Dense"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "execution_count": null,
      "metadata": {
        "id": "PB2uebMR3ida"
      },
      "outputs": [],
      "source": [
        "model=Sequential()"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {
        "id": "eDQYMett4KXa"
      },
      "source": [
        "**ADDING LAYERS**"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {
        "id": "xJJQuw4X4RmM"
      },
      "source": [
        "**CONVOLUTION**"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "execution_count": null,
      "metadata": {
        "id": "c7rSDsG_4WaX"
      },
      "outputs": [],
      "source": [
        "model.add(Convolution2D(32,(3,3),input_shape=(64,64,3),activation='relu'))"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {
        "id": "V8RzfqDJ4cSo"
      },
      "source": [
        "**MAX POOLING**"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "execution_count": null,
      "metadata": {
        "id": "4MR75iuM4izA"
      },
      "outputs": [],
      "source": [
        "model.add(MaxPooling2D(pool_size=(2,2)))"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {
        "id": "V1eNGtw24mxs"
      },
      "source": [
        "**FLATTEN**"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "execution_count": null,
      "metadata": {
        "id": "J-yfaRVU4riM"
      },
      "outputs": [],
      "source": [
        "model.add(Flatten())"
      ]
